Mic5:2 [[But thou, Bethlehem Ephratah, <em>though</em> thou be little among the thousands of Judah, <em>yet</em> out of thee shall he come forth unto me <em>that is</em> to be ruler in Israel; whose goings forth <em>have been</em> from of old, from everlasting.]]
